00:13:34.566 --> 00:13:35.107
AUDIENCE: OK.

00:13:35.107 --> 00:13:35.607
Sure.

00:13:35.607 --> 00:13:36.360
Fine.

00:13:36.360 --> 00:13:36.680
HONG LIU: Yeah.

00:13:36.680 --> 00:13:37.180
Yeah.

