00:50:07.730 --> 00:50:10.700
We find the starting
point, which can be solved.

00:50:10.700 --> 00:50:13.600
Then we expand around
that starting point.

00:50:13.600 --> 00:50:17.490
And that starting point
is often a free theory.

00:50:17.490 --> 00:50:22.430
And then it may expand
upon the free theory.

00:50:22.430 --> 00:50:26.570
So the difficult thing about
this theory is at first,

00:50:26.570 --> 00:50:30.310
it's hard, when you go
to low energies-- first

00:50:30.310 --> 00:50:32.630
it's hard to find
the starting point.

00:50:32.630 --> 00:50:35.330
