00:52:04.271 --> 00:52:06.270
So let's consider that N
goes to infinity limit.

00:52:13.110 --> 00:52:17.180
So he reasoned, if N
goes to infinity limit,

00:52:17.180 --> 00:52:21.880
it's sufficiently simple, then
